start.title: Set up passport renewal notifications
start.intro.banner: This is a demo of what a Passport renewal reminder system could look like.
start.intro:
With this service, you can set up notifications that will automatically inform you when your passport is near the expiry date.

What you’ll need to set up notifications:

  • Your passport number
  • Full name and email address
  • Your passport expiry date (YYYY-MM)
